OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777460574
OL,3,CBag full of 14 abandoned newborn
OL,4,Ckittens found in Atherstone
OL,6,FStreet cleaners have found a bag of 14
OL,7,Fabandoned kittens at a park in North
OL,8,FWarwickshire.
OL,10,FTwo North Warwickshire Borough Council
OL,11,Femployees, named as Carl and Dave,
OL,12,Fwere in the Royal Meadow Drive
OL,13,FRecreational area when they found the
OL,14,Fbag on Saturday morning (25 April).
OL,16,FTen of the kittens were aged
OL,17,Fapproximately four to five weeks, and
OL,18,Ffour were newborn kittens who still
OL,19,Fhad their umbilical cords attached.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777460574
OL,3,CBag full of 14 abandoned newborn
OL,4,Ckittens found in Atherstone
OL,6,FThe kittens were taken to Carl's home
OL,7,Fbefore being taken to The Willows
OL,8,FVeterinary Centre and Referral Service
OL,9,Fin Solihull for assessment and
OL,10,Ftreatment.
OL,12,FNorth Warwickshire Borough Council
OL,13,Fsaid: "Veterinary staff confirmed that
OL,14,Fthe newborn kittens would require
OL,15,Fintensive care, including placement in
OL,16,Fincubators and feeding every three
OL,17,Fhours."
OL,19,FThe council was quick to praise the
OL,20,Factions of the pair on Saturday
OL,21,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
