CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777460574
OL,3,CBag full of 14 abandoned newborn
OL,4,Ckittens found in Atherstone
OL,6,F"North Warwickshire Borough Council
OL,7,Fwould like to commend David and Carl
OL,8,Ffor their quick action,
OL,9,Fprofessionalism and compassion," they
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"And to extend thanks to Carl's family
OL,13,Ffor their immediate support in
OL,14,Fassisting with the animals prior to
OL,15,Fveterinary treatment."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
